{"tid":2432484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政協指學英文浪費時間 提議全國中小學取消必修英文科 「隨著中國經濟社會發展，英語真的有這麼重要嗎？」","createTime":"2021-03-04T11:06:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T11:27:15.000Z","uid":63183,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5cc2aaabb0daeea465d0cd99df47716052c76c76","tid":2432484,"uid":63183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T11:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nxys047.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnxys047.png&h=c5970f93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F5704&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyv9HbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=e551863f\" target=\"_blank\">https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5704</a><br />\n每年全國政協會議及全國人民代表大會「兩會」，唔同政協都會提出議案。有政協委員就建議，要取消全國義務教育（中小學）嘅英文科必修地位，仲要禁止學生參加非官方嘅各種外語考試。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hBSoL0bgwoM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhBSoL0bgwoM&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyv9HbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=0f6bb107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hBSoL0bgwoM</a><br />\n全國政協委員、九三學社中央委員許進話：「為了學英語，學生和家長耗費了大量的時間和精力。但是隨著經濟社會發展，英語真的有這麼重要嗎？」佢指出，美國嘅大學畢業生掌握到3萬至5萬個詞語，但喺中國，識4千個單詞就可以通過大學英語四級考試。為咗讀到「重點中學」，好多小學生都自己去考大學英語4級考試或者更高級嘅英語考試證書。英文教學課時約佔學生總課時嘅10%，但英文只對不到10%嘅大學畢業生有用，所以係成本效益低，課程設置有問題。<br />\n<br />\n許進仲自己研究發現，原來而家啲翻譯機可以提供英文在內多種語言、超過大學英文6級水平嘅口語翻譯服務，技術十分成熟。有咗智能電話嘅翻譯程式，仲好過喺中小學讀咁多年英文。佢又話，喺人工智能時代，翻譯職業已經係即將被淘汰職業嘅頭10名。<br />\n<br />\n佢話好似「音樂、體育和美術」呢啲「素質教育」課程課時太少，如果取消英文做主科，就可以解決缺乏課時嘅問題。「學校應該用充足的時間培養學生的獨立思考能力、實踐能力和創新能力，促進學生全面發展。」<br />\n<br />\n「兩會」今日、聽日喺北京召開，未知許進嘅提案結果如何。不過喺美國，就算係中共嘅死對頭、前國務卿蓬佩奧，都好鼓勵國民讀中文，認為掌握外語先會理解到其他民族國家嘅意圖，睇到「原本睇唔到嘅威脅，降低發生公開衝突嘅可能性」。"},{"pid":"0be4ef5fe326d4b217e2d4f2173ebe0a76e35ff9","tid":2432484,"uid":22422,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T11:08:27.000Z","msg":"有人由小學跳級上博士都只讀中文<br />\n但到最後又咪係通商寬衣 精甚領導<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb037c0ceef5367e5b80a06acd3b0d5002fc1616","tid":2432484,"uid":17765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T11:12:23.000Z","msg":"咁班狗官送後代去美國係讀乜嘢文"},{"pid":"8da8781781535b6cfec945649936761d1e80c605","tid":2432484,"uid":282637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T11:12:54.000Z","msg":"仲停留係洋人船堅炮利思維<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8da59cac00ba2f0f828b899c2cc368ec626476","tid":2432484,"uid":282637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T11:13:22.000Z","msg":"咁漢語拼音呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb8dd9a735fb8e5ad9b14b38dc42cf8330ba638","tid":2432484,"uid":282637,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bb037c0ceef5367e5b80a06acd3b0d5002fc1616","tid":2432484,"uid":17765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T11:12:23.000Z","msg":"咁班狗官送後代去美國係讀乜嘢文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T11:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdkGcpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdkGcpQ.jpg&h=9e04e576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E3kshvu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE3kshvu.png&h=ccb33960&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddfca6bf97fce150fbf8aa0deae7ff84110a05b2","tid":2432484,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T11:18:31.000Z","msg":"拜托香港跟隨  加速加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92b4a0138f0f5c64501d86f2a2372416ae48ca2","tid":2432484,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T11:19:55.000Z","msg":"香港人，仲有咩籍口唔走？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c38ba6f4